data.title: Mad Max Supa-Star Tim Burns takes the Fury Road to Supanova in Sydney this June! Tim is best known for his role as the crazed Johnny the...
data.meta_description:
supanovaexpo on May 22, 2024: "Mad Max Supa-Star Tim Burns takes the Fury Road to Supanova in Sydney this June! 

Tim is best known for his role as the crazed Johnny the Boy in the 1979 classic, Mad Max. Tim also featured in the television series, Patrol Boat, as "Chef" McKinnon, and appeared in The Dismissal, Cop Shop, Glenview High and more! Hungry-eyed Supa-Fans may also spot Tim in Furiosa: A Mad Max Saga, in cinemas now! 

For more info on Tim, visit supa.fans/TBurns

#supanova #sydney #sydnova #supastar #madmax #johnnytheboy #timburns #furiosa #furiosaamadmaxsaga #hungryeyes #convention".
